 London|London]]&nbsp;teams:'''<br />\n[[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]]<br />\n[[Chelsea F.C.|Chelsea]]<br />\n[[Fulham F.C.|Fulham]]<br/>\n[[Queens Park Rangers F.C.|{{nowrap|Queens Park Rangers}}]]<br />\n[[Tottenham Hotspur F.C.|Tottenham&nbsp;Hotspur]]\n|position=right}}\n\n<!--DISPLAY OF GREATER MANCHESTER TEAMS IN UPPER RIGHT CORNER-->\n{{Location map~ |England |mark=TransparentPlaceholder.png |marksize=1 |lat=50.7 |long=-0.8 |label_size=80|label='''[[List of football teams in Greater Manchester|{{nowrap|Greater Manchester}}]]&nbsp;teams:'''<br />\n[[Bolton Wanderers F.C.|{{nowrap|Bolton Wanderers}}]]<br />\n[[Manchester City F.C.|{{nowrap|Manchester City}}]]<br />\n[[Manchester United F.C.|{{nowrap|Manchester United}}]]<br/>\n[[Wigan Athletic F.C.|{{nowrap|Wigan Athletic}}]]|position=right}}\n}}\n\n{{Location map+|Greater London\n |width=300\n |float=right\n |caption=Greater London Premier League football clubs\n |alt=Greater London Premier League football clubs\n |places =\n {{Location map~ |Greater London |lat=51.557311 |long=-0.116789 |mark=Blue pog.svg|label='''[[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]]'''|label_size=75|marksize=|position=top}}\n {{Location map~ |Greater London |lat=51.481667 |long=-0.191111 |mark=Blue pog.svg|label='''[[Chelsea F.C.|Chelsea]]'''|label_size=75|marksize=|position=right}}\n{{Location map~ |Greater London |lat=51.475 |long=-0.221667|mark=Blue pog.svg |label='''[[Fulham F.C.|Fulham]]'''|label_size=75|marksize=|position=bottom}}\n {{Location map~ |Greater London |lat=51.509167 |long=-0.232222|mark=Blue pog.svg |label='''[[Queens Park Rangers F.C.|{{nowrap|Queens Park}}<br/>Rangers]]'''|label_size=75|marksize=|position=left}}\n {{Location map~ |Greater London |lat=51.5974 |long=-0.0716 |mark=Blue pog.svg |label='''[[Tottenham Hotspur F.C.|{{nowrap|Tottenham<br />Hotspur}}]]'''|label_size=75|marksize=|position=top}}\n}}\n\n{{Location map+|Greater Manchester\n |width=300\n |float=right\n |caption=Greater Manchester Premier League football clubs\n |alt=Greater Manchester Premier League football clubs\n |places =\n {{Location map~ |Greater Manchester |lat=53.580578 |long=-2.535644 |mark=Green pog.svg|label='''[[Bolton Wanderers F.C.|Bolton Wanderers]]'''|label_size=75|marksize=|position=top}}\n {{Location map~ |Greater Manchester |lat=53.483139 |long=-2.2003 |mark=Green pog.svg|label='''[[Manchester City F.C.|Manchester City]]'''|label_size=75|marksize=|position=right}}\n{{Location map~ |Greater Manchester |lat=53.463053 |long=-2.291325|mark=Green pog.svg |label='''[[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]]'''|label_size=75|marksize=|position=bottom}}\n {{Location map~ |Greater Manchester |lat=53.547625 |long=-2.654036|mark=Green pog.svg |label='''[[Wigan Athletic F.C.|Wigan Athletic]]'''|label_size=75|marksize=|position=left}}\n}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Team\n! Location\n! Stadium\n! Capacity<ref name=\"PLHandbook\">{{cite web|title=Premier League Handbook Season 2011/12 |url=http://www.premierleague.com/content/dam/premierleague/site-content/News/publications/handbooks/premier-league-handbook-2011-12.pdf |work=PremierLeague.com |publisher=Premier League |accessdate=23 August 2011 |format=PDF |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111204003035/http://www2.premierleague.com/content/dam/premierleague/site-content/News/publications/handbooks/premier-league-handbook-2011-12.pdf |archivedate= 4 December 2011 }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]]\n| [[London]] {{small|([[Holloway, London|Holloway]])}}\n| [[Emirates Stadium]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{Nts|60,361}}\n|-\n| [[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]]\n| [[Birmingham]]\n| [[Villa Park]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{Nts|42,785}}\n|-\n| [[Blackburn Rovers F.C.|Blackburn Rovers]]\n| [[Blackburn]]\n| [[Ewood Park]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{Nts|31,154}}\n|-\n| [[Bolton Wanderers F.C.|Bolton Wanderers]]\n| [[Bolton]]\n| [[Reebok Stadium]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{Nts|28,100}}\n|-\n| [[Chelsea F.C.|Ch